data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. WELCOME TO THE HOUSE OF YOUR DREAMS!!! If you are looking for a property with new and impeccable finishes, this home is for you! In Lakeview Village, it is a great home with nice 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, garage and good curbside parking. You can enjoy your evenings on your oversized covered terrace and in your pool overlooking the pond. Bonus space in the patio of this totally different home, where your family will love to spend quality time cooking and in front of the pool, maintaining a cool area with A/C and comfortable without having to enter your home. The entire house has porcelain and granite in the kitchen and bathrooms as well as the patio, the garage has ceramic tiles and the same as the patio with a screen in the pool. The front of your home is newly remodeled with stone-style ceramics. A/C-New (2022). Convenient location just minutes from I75, schools, restaurants and shopping. Rest assured, this home will fill you with pride and joy when you make it yours. You do NOT want to miss this opportunity! Schedule your visit today!
